{"tid":12817,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「鹹濕」一詞從何而來？跟火腿有關係","createTime":"2016-11-29T21:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T01:37:08.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8bbbe63730d1cba0fe06bd892411a718046cfbfe","tid":12817,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:50:55.000Z","msg":"如果說到跟性愛情色有關的主題，現代人常用「鹹濕」一詞來形容，但你知道「鹹濕」一詞從何而來？<br />\n<br />\n香港《蘋果》報導指出，「鹹濕」一詞源自於廣東，曾一度被廣東妓女拿還來形容「超俗氣的男人」。在1842年第一次鴉片戰爭結束後，上海開港，英、美、法諸國陸續在上海設立租界，西方色情業也進入上海。當時英美人設立色情大腿舞酒吧，並稱之為「hamshop」，上海人一度翻譯為「火腿店」。<br />\n<br />\n不過「hamshop」傳到在上海的廣東人耳裡，「ham」的發音剛好與廣東話「鹹」類似，因此廣東人就戲稱「hamshop」為「鹹濕」，也變成了廣州特有方言詞。（施旖婕／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"eb2c1d072794a519ac5885db76c1cd647b93fe7d","tid":12817,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:01:45.000Z","msg":"施旖婕真係好撚淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc7685fc3aa9a750fbe0a487be091dfa147f066","tid":12817,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:07:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>施旖婕真係好撚淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想同佢做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbd338bc5480ec38a7d86d96cf4de7edb50f1ee4","tid":12817,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:17:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>施旖婕真係好撚淫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想同佢做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n共仔已經痴撚左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d64e8e9813c65368d